1️⃣ User Authentication (JWT)
POST /auth/register → Register new users
POST /auth/login → Authenticate and return token
2️⃣ Portfolio Projects
POST /projects → Add a new project
GET /projects → Get all projects
GET /projects/:id → Get a specific project
PUT /projects/:id → Update a project
DELETE /projects/:id → Delete a project
3️⃣ Work Experience
POST /experience → Add work experience
GET /experience → Get work experience
PUT /experience/:id → Update experience
DELETE /experience/:id → Remove experience
4️⃣ Skills
POST /skills → Add a skill
GET /skills → Get skills list
DELETE /skills/:id → Remove a skill
5️⃣ Contact Form
POST /contact → Save contact messages
GET /contact → View messages (Admin only)